d {$\Lambda$}CDM halo, we find that the spherically averaged density profile becomes progressively shallower from the virial radius inwards, reaching a logarithmic slope shallower than -1.2 at the innermost resolved point, \textasciitilde 0.005 r200, with little evidence for convergence to a power-law behaviour in the inner regions.},
